Package: quantregUtils
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for Quantile Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Renaud", "Mabire", email = "renaud.mabire.yon@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a collection of tools and functions to facilitate quantile regression modeling. Includes functions to check model significance across quantiles, calculate confidence intervals, and test for location shifts. This package aims to simplify the application of quantile regression techniques for researchers and data analysts.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    quantreg,
    stats,
    graphics
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
URL: https://github.com/Renaud-Mabire/quantreg_utils
